The paper discusses a new approach to expressing mutually exclusive clauses in LogicWeb, a logic programming language. This topic is relevant to several subfields of computer science, including artificial intelligence (cs.AI), logic (cs.LO), programming languages (cs.PL), computational linguistics (cs.CL), and machine learning (cs.LG). However, given the focus on logic programming and the use of linear logic connectives, cs.AI and cs.LO are the most likely categories.
